      'At Site Intelligence, we turn around most domestic RSJ calculations within 48 hours. We provide a full specification including beam size, bearing details, padstone requirements, and temporary propping instructions for your builder. We also liaise directly with building control if needed, taking the technical burden off your shoulders so you can focus on the exciting parts of your project.',
